---
title: Island-Spiced Chicken & Roasted Veggies with Tomato Salad & Lemon Aioli
description: We're using our mild Caribbean jerk seasoning to give the classic combo of chicken and veggies some  Jamaican mojo. Colourful veggies with salsa and lemon aioli bring added excitement to this devilishly delicious dish.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/jerk-chicken-roast-veggie-toss-793544f2.jpg
